data.description: Cozy split foyer home with four bedrooms and one and a half baths for sale in Winston Salem! Boasting a practical layout, the main floor hosts the primary bedroom and two others, creating a convenient living space. Downstairs, discover an additional bedroom, a versatile flex space serving as an office, and a spacious family room for relaxation. Updates include modern drywall and plumbing, plus fresh kitchen flooring. All appliances stay, making it move-in ready. Notably, the absence of an HOA provides flexibility, and the 2019-installed metal roof and brick exterior ensure durability and charm. Be sure to schedule your showing today!
